How to add images in our background?
<style type="text/css">
	body {background-image: url(nameoffile);}
     background-repeat:no repeat;                 (gives only single image)
      background-repeat: repeat-x;         (repeat along x-axis)
    background-position: 10px 60px         
                        (right)(down)
                        (we can also use percentage)
</style>

CSS BLOCK MODEL:
Padding-> space b/w text and border
Margin -> space outside border and outside padding
Border-> area that outlines padding
** Padding is inside the border while margin is outside the border


<style type="text/css"> 
h1 {padding: 20px;}
                                          (we can use keyword top,left,right,bottom)
</style>

Border has three property :
border-color: red;
border-width:  3px;
border-style:  dashed;

We can also make different borders in different directions:
border-top-color: ;
